<!DOCTYPE html>
%html
  %head
    %meta{content: "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}
  %body
    .indented.text-center
      %h2= "Hey #{@user.get_name_or_email.capitalize},"

      .text-left
        We wanted to let you know that we're in 
        %a{href: "#{root_url}adventures?state=Hawaii"} Hawaii
        to grow our network of adventurers!
        Our focus remains on continuing to provide unique off-the-beaten-path adventures with amazing hosts from all around the world.

        %br
        %br
        We're looking for 
        %a{href: "#{root_url}about"} story tellers 
        and ways to feature your travels, so lookout for some amazing travel tips and stories in the future!


        %br
        %br
        As always, feel free to send us feedback, trip requests, or just to say aloha! Simply reply to this email.

        %br
        %br
        .divider.divider-border

        %h3.text-center If you're deciding to visit Hawaii, check out our local favorites
        %table#main{border: "0", cellpadding: "0", cellspacing: "20", width: "100%"}
          %tr
            %td
              - adventure = Adventure.find(243)
              %a{href: "#{root_url}adventures/#{adventure.slug}", style: 'text-decoration: none; color: #000;'}
                .adv_img{style: "background: url('#{adventure.attachment.url(:medium)}') center center no-repeat; background-size: cover; width: 150px; height: 125px; margin-left: -25px; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;"}
                .text-left{style: 'word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 12px; width: 150px; margin-left: -25px; font-weight: bold;'}= "#{adventure.title[0..18]}.."
                .text-left{style: 'word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 12px; width: 120px; margin-left: -25px; font-style: italic;'}= "with #{adventure.users.first.get_first_name}"
            %td
              - adventure = Adventure.find(256)
